{"tid":394404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門雙屍案 15歲仔伴母屍一周後斃命","createTime":"2017-09-10T02:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T03:18:11.000Z","uid":3246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d46d4304d9048c824387dd7e3e390fc5283cfa8c","tid":394404,"uid":3246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170910&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57190515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170910%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57190515&d=a5kQm6KhkGVQo82JkK5zbV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e7cd9085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170910%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57190515&h=168f368a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170910&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57190515</a><br />\n<br />\n點解係香港仲可以發生餓死人事件，政府年年收咁多稅都唔攞嚟關心香港市民，只係攞嚟起啲乜撚野幾百億工程，真可悲。房署明知有單位幾個月都無租收都唔理，可以無人上門查，入面班友係咪返工等放工？修身，齊家，治國，平天下，無一個高官做到，個個只係識攞着數，擦鞋，無一個真正想為市民服務...<br />\n<br />\n同埋個大仔同老豆根本就無盡過任何責任，話囇都老婆同阿媽，點解可以咁冷血完全唔理。三年無返過去就話中秋節想返去，屌你老母講大話都唔識講，收完蘋果錢出嚟做訪問就想變孝子？<br />\n<br />\n最後俾個贊收數佬，知道母子無野食都買盒飯俾佢地<br />\n<br />\n聽講個大仔Fb名叫紅連，大家可以問下佢覺唔覺得老母生舊叉燒好過生佢"},{"pid":"9967e9ea803508b635553931497fbefb7680ecc5","tid":394404,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"香港人狗也不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸人又可以呃綜援呃學位 呃身份有得輸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3ec60c6ce5dd8fe444e88e743e8d944fdcfaff","tid":394404,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使唔使同一單新聞兩日內開咁多post"}]}